  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Getaway Storm</strong> is a simple fun arcade racing game that quickly turns into online multiplayer chaos with friends! Surviving for as long as you can is a team effort, since anyone getting wrecked is a game over for everyone. Let's see how fast you can go and how long you can last. 😎 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer with 1-5 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade handling/drifting physics that are just built different 😎</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Audio Drive mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 sus cars to unlock and drive 😳 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of car crashes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highscore and replay system with different categories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weekly and Daily online leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Getaway Storm</strong> is a simple fun arcade racing game that quickly turns into online multiplayer chaos with friends! Surviving for as long as you can is a team effort, since anyone getting wrecked is a game over for everyone. Let's see how fast you can go and how long you can last. 😎 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer with 1-5 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade handling/drifting physics that are just built different 😎</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Audio Drive mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 sus cars to unlock and drive 😳 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of car crashes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highscore and replay system with different categories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weekly and Daily online leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
